Package com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.event

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackgroundEvent
    This event is posted to the EventBus when the application goes into the background for more than a minute seconds, or when the application has come back into the foreground.
    BeaconRegionEnterEvent
    This event is posted to the EventBus when the device enters a beacon region.
    BeaconRegionExitEvent
    This event is posted to the EventBus when the device exits a beacon region.
    BeaconRegionRangeEvent
    This event is posted to the EventBus when the device ranges a beacon.
    BeaconResponseEvent
    This event is posted via the EventBus.
    CloudPagesChangedEvent
    This event is posted to the EventBus when the application has received new CloudPage messages from the server.
    EtAnalyticItemEvent  
    GeofenceResponseEvent
    This event is posted via the EventBus.
    LastKnownLocationEvent
    EventBus low-level sticky notification event that occurs whenever we come into the foreground or whenever the 5000m fence (aka the Magic Fence) is crossed.
    LocationStatusEvent
    This event is posted to the EventBus when the status of location watching changes
    PowerStatusChangedEvent
    This event is posted via the EventBus.
    ProximityStatusEvent
    This event is posted to the EventBus when the status of proximity watching changes
    PushReceivedEvent
    This event is posted via the EventBus.
    PushStatusEvent
    This event is posted to the EventBus when the status of pushEnabled changes
    ReadyAimFireInitCompletedEvent
    This event is posted via the EventBus.
    RegistrationEvent
    This event is posted via the EventBus.
    ServerErrorEvent
    This event is posted via the EventBus.
    SilentPushReceivedEvent
    This event is posted via the EventBus.
